featured_reviews.review_id: An entirely different aspect of the Sikh faith, wherein it acts as an anchor for all the world religions, Gobind Sadan is a visionary and absolutely relevant place in today's context. Founded by Baba Virsa Singh ji, it is a large sanctuary of sorts. A must visit if you are interested or inclined spiritually, along with a curiosity for coexistence of different faiths.
